FREELANCE SPY: Intelligence broker without a flag

A Freelance Spy sells information and intelligence to the highest
bidder, working without permanent affiliation to any single faction.
In the Rifts world of competing powers, a skilled spy with no loyalty
is highly employable.

Freelance Spies choose from Espionage, Rogue, Technical, and Physical
skill categories. They are trained in surveillance, disguise,
intelligence gathering, and discreet communication. Combat is a last
resort.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: IQ 11, MA 10, PP 10.
  Equipment: Concealed recording device, encrypted communicator, two
    changes of civilian clothing, a concealed sidearm, forged
    credentials, and working capital for bribes.

